AHC-HRSN-screening-example.name: AHCHRSNScreening
AHC-HRSN-screening-example.description: This is a SDC Questionnaire example that represents the *US Core Observation Screening Assessment Profile* AHC-HRSN defined in LOINC (code 96777-8)). This example contains no actual questions, but is used to provide metadata about the assessment tool.
